Author : JEEN < jeen@perl.kr >
Title : Delicious Library 2 for Aladdin / Korean

* ATTENTION
 you must install these modules.
  - Mac::AppleScript
  - WebService::Aladdin
  - AnyEvent (for iSight Capture)
  - HTTP::Engine (for Bookmarklet)

* scripts
- bin/term.pl
 1. Run Delicious Library 2
 2. run 'perl bin/term.pl' in Terminal
 3. Input your Item's Code (ISBN)

- bin/isight.pl
 1. Run Delicious Library 2
 2. run 'perl bin/isight.pl' in Terminal
 3. Capture a barcode by Mac's iSight

- bin/server.pl
 1. Run Delicious Library 2
 2. run 'perl bin/server-starter.pl' in Terminal
 3. Install a Bookmarklet for DL2 
 4. open http://www.aladdin.co.kr/shop/wproduct.aspx?ISBN=.*
 5. click the Bookmarklet Button
